OL,3,CSmall business loses thousands after
OL,4,CFacebook page hacked
OL,6,FA clothing company in Maidenhead say
OL,7,Fthey've lost thousands of pounds of
OL,8,Fbusiness after their Facebook account
OL,9,Fwas taken over by hackers.
OL,11,FStaff at SP Workwear say they were
OL,12,Flocked out of their page overnight and
OL,13,Fare unable to access their valuable
OL,14,Fsocial media profile and customer base.
OL,16,FThey're now warning other small
OL,17,Fbusinesses to be extra vigilant.
OL,19,FMeta, who own Facebook, say they take
OL,20,Fthe safety and security of their users
OL,21,Fseriously.
