OL,6,FTwo months ago, SP Workwear's Facebook
OL,7,Faccount was taken over by hackers and
OL,8,Fthree fraudulent payments of #700
OL,9,Fappeared on their credit card account.
OL,11,F"Overnight an email came through to
OL,12,Fsay so and so is now an admin on your
OL,13,Faccount," said SP Workwear director,
OL,14,FSteve Palmer.
OL,16,F"I didn't think too much of it as we
OL,17,Fwork with an ad agency so we were
OL,18,Fdiscussing some changes."
