OL,6,F"The next day we were trying to post
OL,7,Fsomething and it wasn't working, it
OL,8,Fkept coming up with an error."
OL,10,F"We went in and realised we couldn't
OL,11,Faccess the back end of the website and
OL,12,Feveryone who was an admin has been
OL,13,Fkicked off."
OL,15,FThe company which supplies branded
OL,16,Fworkwear was reassured by Meta that
OL,17,Fthe issue would be quickly resolved
OL,18,Fbut several weeks on Mr Palmer says
OL,19,Fthey still can't access their Facebook
OL,20,Faccount.
