OL,6,F"Social media is used for that more
OL,7,Fcasual way of connecting with your
OL,8,Fcustomers. having that taken away you
OL,9,Fjust don't have it," said digital
OL,10,Fmarketing apprentice Charlotte Millar.
OL,12,FThe initial losses were recouped but
OL,13,Fthe company estimates the blocked
OL,14,Fsocial media account has cost them
OL,15,Faround #20,000 in lost revenue.
