OL,6,FA spokesman for Meta said: "Fraudulent
OL,7,Factivity is not allowed on our
OL,8,Fplatforms and we are continually
OL,9,Finvesting in new technologies to
OL,10,Ftackle this industry-wide issue. We
OL,11,Ftake the safety and security of our
OL,12,Fcommunity seriously."
OL,14,FMr Palmer doesn't know how the breach
OL,15,Fhappened but is warning other small
OL,16,Fbusinesses to restrict access to
OL,17,Fsocial media accounts and make ensure
OL,18,Fsecurity measures are in place.
